data.description: Welcome home to this sweet upgraded single level move in ready home with 3 beds in gated community of Lake Holiday. New ext paint, new (5 yr old) roof, new LVP floors all thru, great lot with view of trees & spacious back yard, home is set back perfectly on lot. Fireplace w/insert, new water heater, good size kitchen with plenty of cabinet space, Community lake access, stocked for fishing, kayaking & swimming, playground, sport court, club house can be rented for large events, Slider off dining area opens to patio and wonderful back yard setting awaiting your personal touches or leave as is for low maintenance. Lake Holiday is a great place to live, box stores, restaurants, hospital in nearby Gig Harbor. Water is included in HOA dues.
